ìGremlins&quot; </span><![endif]--><!--[if supportFields]><span

style='font-size:10.0pt'><span style='mso-element:field-end'></span></span><![endif]--><span

style='font-size:10.0pt'>&quot;, &quot;New&quot; you'll be given the chance to

create a New Gremlin Horde (<span class=SpellE>POSE's</span> nomenclature, not

mine!) that will run any application or group of applications.<span

style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>You can also determine how many times to run

each app, and how to log the different events, errors, and activities that

might occur.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><o:p></o:p></span></p>



