style='font-size:10.0pt'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span>machine that's

running POSE.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>One should be already set

up to run HotSync.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>In order to allow

POSE to HotSync on this machine, right click on POSE, select

&quot;Settings&quot;, &quot;Properties&quot;, and under &quot;</span><st1:place><st1:PlaceName><span

  style='font-size:10.0pt'>Serial</span></st1:PlaceName><span style='font-size:

 10.0pt'> </span><st1:PlaceType><span style='font-size:10.0pt'>Port</span></st1:PlaceType></st1:place><span

